ila pia hii login page haijakaa kiproffesional kabisa yani ni mbaya hebu jaribu kunidesgnia nyingine kali na nzuri na pia iwe ya kisasa kabisa yenye kuvutia sio kama hiyo pia iwe responsive for all devices.
pia tumia background image nzuri ambayo itafanya contnets ziwe zinaonekana vizuri  lakini pia icons kwenye kila fieds na pia badala ya kutumia username tumia email, then nipe full codes inthe same screen.
